{"tid":1862994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】曾載港確診翁郵輪　船上10人確診　逾200人有發燒等徵狀","createTime":"2020-02-05T02:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T02:58:53.000Z","uid":73915,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b6af56ea69fef49d8fbf80404cb143e1b61c40bb","tid":1862994,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T02:27:18.000Z","msg":"【09:40更新】日本厚生勞動省今早（5日）公布，香港確診80歲男子曾乘坐、前日返抵橫濱並須隔離檢疫的「鑽石公主號」郵輪，船上10人確診感染新型冠狀病毒肺炎，有人出現發燒等徵狀。<br />\n<br />\n厚生勞動省補充，確診的10人已送往醫院接受隔離治療；船上有逾200人出現發燒等徵狀，尚待檢測結果。"},{"pid":"28e1b0bad7a6dbbeefcccdedf8acf242ffdbe746","tid":1862994,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"200<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6705c22c12c732c74692d73603e11aa2fb2d0c61","tid":1862994,"uid":119596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"holy shit<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eba3cdf77dcdc2076d6afa8ccf080ead3ce40a","tid":1862994,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"明報譯錯，日本啲新聞都係話咳/發燒/同病人有密切接觸者初步有273個人，唔係200幾個人發燒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom: 産経新聞<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20200205-00000509-san-hlth\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20200205-00000509-san-hlth&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3fUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=b5928d13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20200205-00000509-san-hlth</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom: 朝日新聞<br />